# 🤖 PSX Marketing Bot — Setup Guide

Automatically generates and posts 3 PSX trading content posts per day to your Facebook page using real news + OpenAI.

---

## 📁 Files Overview

```
psx_marketing_bot/
├── main.py              ← Run this to start the bot
├── news_scraper.py      ← Fetches PSX news from RSS feeds
├── post_generator.py    ← Uses OpenAI to write Facebook posts
├── facebook_poster.py   ← Posts to your Facebook page
├── requirements.txt     ← Python packages needed
├── .env.example         ← Config template (rename to .env)
└── logs/                ← All drafts and logs saved here
```

---

## ⚡ STEP 1 — Install Python & Dependencies

Make sure Python 3.10+ is installed, then run:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

## ⚡ STEP 2 — Set Up Your .env File

1. Rename `.env.example` to `.env`
2. Fill in your keys (see below for how to get them)

```
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
FACEBOOK_PAGE_ID=...
FACEBOOK_ACCESS_TOKEN=...
AUTO_POST=false           ← change to true when ready
WHATSAPP_GROUP_LINK=https://chat.whatsapp.com/your-link
```

---

## ⚡ STEP 3 — Get Your OpenAI API Key

1. Go to https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
2. Click "Create new secret key"
3. Copy and paste into `.env`

💡 Estimated cost: ~$5-8/month for 3 posts/day using GPT-4.1-mini

---

## ⚡ STEP 4 — Get Your Facebook Page Access Token

### One-time Setup:

1. Go to https://developers.facebook.com/apps
2. Click "Create App" → Choose "Business"
3. Under "Add Products", add **Pages API**
4. Go to **Tools → Graph API Explorer**
5. Select your App from the dropdown
6. Select your Page from "User or Page" dropdown
7. Add permissions: `pages_manage_posts`, `pages_read_engagement`
8. Click "Generate Access Token"
9. Copy the token into `.env` as `FACEBOOK_ACCESS_TOKEN`
10. Get your Page ID: Go to your Facebook Page → About → Page ID

### Get Long-Lived Token (DO THIS — avoids daily re-login):

Run this once in Python:

```python
from facebook_poster import get_long_lived_token
get_long_lived_token(
    app_id="YOUR_APP_ID",
    app_secret="YOUR_APP_SECRET",
    short_token="YOUR_SHORT_TOKEN"
)
```

Save the output token in `.env`. It lasts 60 days.

---

## ⚡ STEP 5 — Test the Bot (Safe — No Posting)

```bash
python main.py --test
```

This will:
- Fetch real PSX news ✅
- Generate all 3 posts using OpenAI ✅
- Print them to screen and save to logs/ ✅
- NOT post to Facebook ✅

Check `logs/` folder to review the drafts.

---

## ⚡ STEP 6 — Post Manually (First Real Test)

```bash
# Post all 3 right now
python main.py --post now

# Post only morning post
python main.py --post morning
```

---

## ⚡ STEP 7 — Run the Auto Scheduler

When you are happy with the posts, enable auto-posting:

1. Set `AUTO_POST=true` in `.env`
2. Run the scheduler:

```bash
python main.py
```

The bot will now post automatically at:
- **08:30 AM** → Morning Briefing
- **01:00 PM** → Midday Market Update  
- **07:00 PM** → Evening Recap + FOMO

---

## 🖥️ Run 24/7 on a Server (Optional)

To keep the bot running even when you close your laptop:

### Option A — Windows Task Scheduler
Create a task that runs `python main.py` at startup.

### Option B — Linux/Mac with screen
```bash
screen -S psx-bot
python main.py
# Press Ctrl+A then D to detach
```

### Option C — Free Hosting (Railway.app)
1. Push this folder to a GitHub repo
2. Connect to Railway.app (free tier)
3. Set environment variables in Railway dashboard
4. Deploy

---

## 📋 Daily Log Files

Every post is saved in `logs/` as a JSON file:
```
logs/morning_20260424_0830.json
logs/midday_20260424_1300.json
logs/evening_20260424_1900.json
logs/bot.log  ← Full activity log
```

---

## 🛠️ Customization

### Change posting times:
Edit in `.env`:
```
POST_TIME_1=09:00
POST_TIME_2=12:30
POST_TIME_3=18:00
```

### Change post style/tone:
Edit `SYSTEM_PROMPT` in `post_generator.py`

### Add more news sources:
Add RSS URLs to `RSS_FEEDS` dict in `news_scraper.py`

---

## ❓ Troubleshooting

| Problem | Solution |
|---------|----------|
| `openai` import error | Run `pip install openai` |
| Facebook token expired | Generate new token, update `.env` |
| No news fetched | Check your internet connection |
| Posts not generating | Check your OpenAI API key and balance |
| Facebook post fails | Verify PAGE_ID is correct (numbers only) |

